parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the catalytic converter can cause the engine to stall or catch fire, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the vehicle loses power
the vehicle shakes when pressing the brakes
the engine light stays on
the vehicle won't start
the engine makes a knocking noise
the vehicle accelerates poorly
smoke fills the cabin
and oil consumption increases.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive engine oil consumption can cause the catalytic converter to fail, leading to engine stall or fire, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle consumes excessive amounts of oil
the oil level drops rapidly
and the engine makes a knocking noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling or failure can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, particularly if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails
the vehicle loses power
and the vehicle won't start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, catch fire, or experience other safety issues, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine light is illuminated
the vehicle hesitates or stalls
the oil light is illuminated
the battery warning light is illuminated
the vehicle experiences abnormal rattling or knocking noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the catalytic converter can cause the vehicle to experience poor engine performance, decreased fuel efficiency, and potentially lead to engine failure or fires.
symptoms: The check engine light is illuminated
the vehicle experiences poor engine performance
decreased fuel efficiency
abnormal rattling or knocking noises
the catalytic converter warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to experience difficulty shifting gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle experiences difficulty shifting gears
the transmission warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights and electrical system can cause the vehicle to experience reduced visibility, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The headlights turn off or flicker
the electrical system warning light is illuminated
the vehicle experiences abnormal electrical system behavior.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to experience sudden loss of power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine warning light is illuminated
the vehicle experiences sudden loss of power
abnormal rattling or knocking noises
the engine fails to start.
